{"tid":382110,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦關機問題","createTime":"2017-08-31T12:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T13:44:50.000Z","uid":16387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"592214ab51083bb2997e61da82ae98a61896bce6","tid":382110,"uid":16387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"部電腦近幾個禮拜開始打機時會斷電熄機<br />\n例如玩PUBG玩左陣會熄 但玩需求低既game就無事（eg.fallout new vega)<br />\n唔知係咪火牛問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下有冇巴打知係咩問題<br />\n<br />\nspecs:<br />\ndisplay card:gtx 1060 gaming x 6gb<br />\n火牛:gx550<br />\n底板:b150 m3<br />\ncpu:i7 6670<br />\n<br />\n可正常開機 上網睇片 但一玩需求高既game就會斷左電<br />\ncpu並冇過熱<br />\n機齡:半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fde3875a69aecb032826f1188a82b765e97f93","tid":382110,"uid":16387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:44:50.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}